body:
**This mod will help you create different maps.**

## **New items!**
Super sword - will help to kill any entity;
Mega regeneration potion - Will help you heal in a couple of seconds;
Switch the mode to creative;
Switch the mode to survival;
Set day;
Set night;
Kill all;
Kill the bats;
Highlight all players;
Clear Inventory;
Remove effects;
Switch mode to spectator;
Switch mode to adventure;
Set clear weather;
Set rain;
Set thunder;
Turn on God mode;
Teleport to a nearby player.

**The mod was created only to help create maps, the mod is not suitable for a survival game.**

Made in MCreator
